value.name: Resident: Story of 5 Interns
value.original_name: レジデント〜5人の研修医
value.overview: Patients are brought in one after the other. Being put in an environment where there is a race against time to save lives, all they can do is stand there doing nothing. Though they still have a lot to grow as a doctor and as individuals, will they be able to overcome adversity and one day be able to proudly identify themselves as being a doctor?
